Detailed Description

A category which answers questions about attribute capability for a Stark.

Member Function Documentation

+ (NSAttributeType) attributeTypeForKey: (NSString *)  key  

Returns the attribute type for a given attribute key.

Attribute types for managed attributes are determined by consulting the receiver's managed object context.  Attribute types for some other attributes are hard-coded.  If key is nil, returns NSUndefinedAttributeType.

- (BOOL) canHaveChildren
